---
By: Dalai Lama
Source:
  URL: https://twitter.com/DalaiLama/status/985812553870774272
  Locus:
    Date: 16 Apr 2018
---
Compassion reduces our fear, boosts our confidence, and opens us to inner
strength. By reducing distrust, it opens us to others and brings us a
sense of connections with them and a sense of purpose and meaning in life.
